 "title": "Broccoli chicken – my kids' favourite",
 "excerpt": "I can win my family over in a flash with this chicken. Of all the food in Foodland, it's their favourite – and mine too. This dish can beat back plenty of hunger pangs. It's enough for 8 to 10 people (when the family comes to visit). Halve it if it's just the 4 of you.",
