 },
 "html": "<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">I can win my family over in a flash with this chicken. Of all the food in Foodland, it's their favourite &#8211; and mine too.  This dish can beat back plenty of hunger pangs. It's enough for 8 to 10 people (when the family comes to visit). Halve it if it's just the 4 of you.</p>\n\n\n<div data-recipe-slot=\"1\"></div>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/broccoli-hoender-blog-012.jpg\"><img src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/broccoli-hoender-blog-012-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"broccoli hoender blog 012\" class=\"wp-image-628\" loading=\"lazy\"></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/broccoli-hoender-blog-112.jpg\"><img src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/broccoli-hoender-blog-112-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"broccoli hoender blog 112\" class=\"wp-image-641\" loading=\"lazy\"></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">If you don't know it well yet, you're about to. It tastes even better the next day. I serve my broccoli chicken with rice. That's how I make my kids' hearts happy.</p>",
